---
<style>
  [follower-card="regular"].hover-attributes:hover {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }
  [follower-card="regular"].hover-attributes ["follower-card-border"] > img {
    opacity: 0;
  }
  [follower-card="regular"].hover-attributes:hover ["follower-card-border"] > img {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>

<Card
